/***************************************
Jazz Public Environment Variables 
***************************************/
To set an environment variable from the UNIX prompt:
%setenv <variable> <value>


RDS_CDS_VERIFY_TECH
  -Defines the process technology for design and verification 

RDS_CDS_PSF_WARN
  -Possible values: Yes, No
  -Default value: Yes
  -Upon closing the simulation window, sets whether the user is asked if they want to delete 
	the contents of their current run's psf directory. 


/***************************************
Jazz Public SKILL Functions
***************************************/

jazzPubRegUserTriggers(viewType userAppTrigger userMenuTrigger userPostInstallTrigger "tggg")
  -Public function for registering userApp, userMenu, and userPostInstall triggers
  -Maintains a list of all loaded triggers

rdsSchCbrSetIncludes(includeFiles "t")
  -Public function for setting default CBR netlister include files.
  -Provide one or more include files in a space-delimited string.

rdsSchCbrGetIncludes()
  -Public function for getting default CBR netlister include files.
  -Returns space-delimited CBR netlister include files or empty string.

rdsSchCdlCompCall()
  -Custom Cdl netlister function for primitives

rdsSchSubcktCall()
  -Custom Cdl netlister function for subcircuits

jazzModelAddDir(modelDir "t") 
  - Public function to add a modelDir to the list of model libraries in the Jazz
    Model Corner form in ADE. modelDir must be a fully-qualified path that
	 contains the simulator directory.

